@node Descrizione " Description "
Amiga on Line is the first italian WEB-magazine for Amiga games, from this
number it is also full english.
In Amiga on line number 2 you can find:

	NEWS:
-Vulcan new titles for 1997,
-Foundation first look,
-Wendetta first look,
-Mirage software (Poland) new Amiga titles,
-New soccer game announced...

	PREVIEWS:
-Chaos Engine 2,
-Gnomes,
-Jet Pilot,
-Hellpigs,
-Trapped,
-Virtual Karting Deluxe...

	REVIEWS:
-Kick Off 96,
-Blobz,
-Breed 2000,
-Bograts,
-Spherical Worlds,
-DNA,
-Ruffian,
-Fields of Battle...

And also our Tips section, our HOT Links and the reader's Top Ten.

@endnode   
@node Installazione " How to use these files "
            
To view and browse trough Amiga On Line number 2 you have to run your 
browser ( AMosaic, AWeb, Voyager, ALynx or IBrowse (recommended)) and
load the local file "index.html", that is located in Amy on Line disk
or in the HD partition where you moved Amy on Line disk' files.    

